Symbol.Script_3D:
sectWidth=sectWidth/1000 sectDepth=sectDepth/1000 sectThick=sectThick/1000 flangeThick=flangeThick/1000 Rad=Rad/1000 RRadius=Rad
IF gs_shadow=0 THEN SHADOW OFF ELSE SHADOW ON ENDIF
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 THEN END
PEN gs_cont_pen MATERIAL col_mat
IF iInsertPoint = INSERTPOINT_CENTER THEN ADDz -sectDepth/2 IF iInsertPoint = INSERTPOINT_TOP THEN ADDz -sectDepth
IF iArcResolType = ARCRES_SEGMNUM THEN !! ARC RESOL CALCULATION TempArcResol=SegNum ELSE TempArcResol = max(1, INT ((2*ArcRadius*PI/SegLength)*(ArcAngle/360))) ENDIF
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 OR GLOB_CONTEXT>20 and GLOB_CONTEXT<40 THEN !!3D FEEDBACK AT HOTSPOT EDITING = SIMPLE MODEL
FOR i=-1 TO TempArcResol+1 STEP 1 PUT ArcRadius*COS(ArcAngle*i/TempArcResol) PUT ArcRadius*SIN(ArcAngle*i/TempArcResol) PUT 0 PUT 0 NEXT i
TUBE 12,TempArcResol+3,1+2+16+32, -sectWidth/2,0,0, sectWidth/2,0,0, sectWidth/2,flangeThick,0, sectThick/2,flangeThick,0, sectThick/2,sectDepth-flangeThick,0, sectWidth/2,sectDepth-flangeThick,0, sectWidth/2,sectDepth,0, -sectWidth/2,sectDepth,0, -sectWidth/2,sectDepth-flangeThick,0, -sectThick/2,sectDepth-flangeThick,0, -sectThick/2,flangeThick,0, -sectWidth/2,flangeThick,0, GET(nsp)
ELSE
!!! Curved Resolution S=90/gs_resol FOR k=0 TO 90 STEP S PUT sectThick/2+Rad-Rad*sin(k),flangeThick+Rad-Rad*cos(k),1 NEXT k FOR k=90 TO 180 STEP S PUT sectThick/2+Rad-Rad*sin(k),sectDepth-flangeThick-Rad-Rad*cos(k),1 NEXT k FOR k=180 TO 90 STEP -S PUT -sectThick/2-Rad+(Rad)*sin(k),sectDepth-flangeThick-Rad-(Rad)*cos(k),1 NEXT k FOR k=90 TO 0 STEP -S PUT -sectThick/2-Rad+(Rad)*sin(k),flangeThick+Rad-(Rad)*cos(k),1 NEXT k
FOR i=-1 TO TempArcResol+1 STEP 1 PUT ArcRadius*COS(ArcAngle*i/TempArcResol) PUT ArcRadius*SIN(ArcAngle*i/TempArcResol) PUT 0 PUT 0 NEXT i
TUBE 8+(NSP-4*(TempArcResol+3))/3,TempArcResol+3,1+2+16+32, -sectWidth/2,0,0, sectWidth/2,0,0, sectWidth/2,flangeThick,0, GET((NSP-4*(TempArcResol+3))/4), GET((NSP-4*(TempArcResol+3))/3), sectWidth/2,sectDepth-flangeThick,0, sectWidth/2,sectDepth,0, -sectWidth/2,sectDepth,0, -sectWidth/2,sectDepth-flangeThick,0, GET((NSP-4*(TempArcResol+3))/2), GET((NSP-4*(TempArcResol+3))), -sectWidth/2,flangeThick,0,
GET(nsp) ENDIF
unID=1
!!! ARC ANGLE HOTSPOT 0,0,sectDepth/2,unID,ArcAngle,6 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT (ArcRadius),0,sectDepth/2,unID,ArcAngle,4+256 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT (ArcRadius)*cos(ArcAngle),(ArcRadius)*sin(ArcAngle),sectDepth/2,unID,ArcAngle,5 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0,0,sectDepth, unID, ArcAngle,7 : unID=unID+1
!!! Htps at section FOR kk=1 to 2 ADDx ArcRadius HOTSPOT -sectWidth/2,0,0,unID : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT sectWidth/2,0,0,unID : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT 0,0,ZZYZX,unID : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -sectWidth/2,0,ZZYZX,unID : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT sectWidth/2,0,ZZYZX,unID : unID=unID+1 DEL 1 ROTz ArcAngle NEXT kk DEL 2
!!!LENGHT HOTSPOT 0,0,0,unID,ArcRadius,1+256 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT ArcRadius,0,0,unID,ArcRadius, 2 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -1,0,0,unID,ArcRadius,3 : unID=unID+1
ROTz ArcAngle HOTSPOT 0,0,0,unID,ArcRadius,1+256 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT ArcRadius,0,0,unID,ArcRadius, 2 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -1,0,0,unID,ArcRadius,3 : unID=unID+1 DEL 1
IF iInsertPoint = INSERTPOINT_CENTER THEN DEL 1 IF iInsertPoint = INSERTPOINT_TOP THEN DEL 1
Symbol.Script_2D:
File_Dependence "IPE(14).txt" ! --- for using in parameters script
sectWidth=sectWidth/1000 sectDepth=sectDepth/1000 sectThick=sectThick/1000 flangeThick=flangeThick/1000 Rad=Rad/1000 RRadius=Rad
unID=1 hLineID = 1000
!!! ARC RADIUS ROT2 ArcAngle/2 HOTSPOT2 0,0,unID,ArcRadius,1 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 ArcRadius,0,unID,ArcRadius,2 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -1,0,unID,ArcRadius,3 : unID=unID+1 DEL 1
!!! ARC ANGLE HOTSPOT2 0,0,unID,ArcAngle,6 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 (ArcRadius),0,unID,ArcAngle,4+256 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 (ArcRadius)*cos(ArcAngle),(ArcRadius)*sin(ArcAngle),unID,ArcAngle,5 : unID=unID+1
IF (axis=1) THEN
PEN axis_line_pen LINE_TYPE axis_line_type ARC2 0,0,ArcRadius,0,ArcAngle HOTARC2 0,0,ArcRadius,0,ArcAngle, hLineID
ENDIF
IF axis=1 AND only_axis=0 OR axis=0 THEN
PEN gs_cont_pen FILL gs_fill_type LINE_TYPE 1
IF ABS(ArcAngle-360)<EPS THEN !! ArcAngle = 360
POLY2_b 4, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0, 0, 900, (ArcRadius+sectWidth/2), 360, 4001, 0, 0, 900, (ArcRadius-sectWidth/2), 360, 4001
ELSE
POLY2_b 7, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, ArcRadius+sectWidth/2, 0, 1, 0,0,900, 0,ArcAngle,4001, (ArcRadius-sectWidth/2)*COS(ArcAngle),(ArcRadius-sectWidth/2)*SIN(ArcAngle),1, 0,0,900, 0,-ArcAngle,4001, ArcRadius-sectWidth/2, 0, -1
ENDIF
IF gs_ShowMoreHtps2D=1 THEN HOTSPOT2 ArcRadius-sectWidth/2,0,unID : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 ArcRadius+sectWidth/2,0,unID : unID=unID+1
ROT2 ArcAngle HOTSPOT2 ArcRadius-sectWidth/2,0,unID : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 ArcRadius+sectWidth/2,0,unID : unID=unID+1 DEL 1 ENDIF
ENDIF

if Profile<>`СПЕЦИАЛЬНЫЕ` & Profile <> lastProfile then
lastProfile = Profile parameters lastProfile = Profile
szelv=open("text", "IPE(14).txt", "separator='\t', mode=ro, Library") File_Dependence "IPE(14).txt" for i=2 to sor+1 n=input(szelv, i, 2, ker) if Profile=ker then n=input(szelv, i, 3, omassm, ods, ows, owt, oft, orr, oas, ohi, odbf, osmix, oewx, opwx, orix, osmiy, oewy, opwy, oriy ) i=sor+1 ! force loop end endif next i close szelv

ENDIF
